content: WEBSITE                       TWITTER                     TELEGRAM                      FACEBOOK                 BOUNTY GROUP 1. The Bounty campaign will be managed by Worsh Bitcointalk.2. 150000 Tokens are to be divided according to the stakes accumulated amongst selected participants.3. The bounty program was launched on September 13rd, 2023 and will run until October 12th, 2023.1. All participants must join Meta Trade official Telegram Channel,  Telegram Group,2. All participants must join Worsh Bitcointalk Telegram Group, Telegram Channel,3. Talking about the bounty program in the project chat group will lead to immediate disqualification from the campaign andan instant ban from the company chat group. Please ask your bounty-related questions in the Worsh BitcointalkBounty Group,4. KYC is not required for the bounty campaign. However, the project's team has the right to require KYC for suspicious cases.5. Please note that any offensive or inappropriate behavior will lead to immediate disqualification from the campaign.6. Using multiple accounts, cheating and spamming are not allowed. You will be disqualified from the bounty programimmediately and all your accounts will be banned permanently. Brand new accounts are not allowed to join.7. Participants with a minimum of 50+ activity counts on Bitcointalk will be eligible to join the campaigns while,8. Participants can not change their wallet address after registration. Please double check your wallet address beforeregistration for any campaign.Twitter              60%Telegram          40%Note: Due to the bounty duration and pool, we have limited the number of participants for this bounty.Twitter:  First 150 approved participants.Telegram: First 100 approved participants.Week 1 (13.09 - 19.09)Week 2 (20.09 - 27.09) Week 3 (28.09 - 05.10) Week 4 (06.10 - 12.10) --> Please submit your weekly report on this bounty thread <--Rewards:1. Have more than 501 followers: 1 stake/week2. Have more than 1501 followers: 2 stakes/week3. Have more than 5001 followers: 3 stakes/week4. Have more than 10,001 followers: 4 stakes/weekRules:  1. Every participant must follow Meta Trade Twitter Page.2. Twitter accounts must have a minimum of 501 followers.3. Participants have to make new tweets or retweet 5 tweets per week (maximum 1 retweet/day).4. Time gap between 2 retweets/tweets needs to be 10 hours minimum.5. Participants must use #Meta #Trade #Coinsbit #Listing hashtags in every retweet or tweet.Fill the registration form: Rewards:5 stakes/weekRules:1. Update your Telegram name to "Your Name |  Meta Trade''. Only one project is allowed in your Telegram name.2. Replace your profile picture with Meta Trade Logo  .3. Write at least 5 constructive messages in other crypto-related telegram groups.Posts/messages must be constructive, useful and in a way which will not be considered as spamming.4. Deleted messages will not be counted.5. Report your telegram message links weekly. Please obey the report dates and format.6. You must stay in the telegram group until the end of the campaign to receive your stakes.7. You must wear Meta Trade avatar and text until the end of the campaign to receive your stakes.Fill the registration form:
